## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.11+
- Poetry
- OpenAI API key

### Setup

```bash
# Clone and install
git clone <repository-url>
cd AgentOps
pip install -e .

# Set environment variables
export OPENAI_API_KEY="your-api-key"
```

### Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=agentops_ai

# Run linting
ruff check agentops_ai
black --check agentops_ai
```

### Documentation

```bash
# Start documentation server
cd agentops_ai/docs
mkdocs serve
```

